      "id": "PopularPost109943",
      "post_content": "Banding, yes. And at instant speed. As if banding wasn't complicated enough. The Helm is a healthy addition to any deck, at a reasonable casting cost and activation cost. Use the Helm with regenerators like [Uthden Troll](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Uthden Troll), [Drudge Skeletons](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Drudge Skeletons), and [Wall of Brambles](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wall of Brambles) and your army will never die.",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost109943\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Banding, yes.  And at instant speed.  As if banding wasn't complicated enough.  The Helm is a healthy addition to any deck, at a reasonable casting cost and activation cost.  Use the Helm with regenerators like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Uthden Troll\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Uthden Troll\">Uthden Troll</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Drudge Skeletons\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Drudge Skeletons\">Drudge Skeletons</a>, and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wall of Brambles\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wall of Brambles\">Wall of Brambles</a> and your army will never die.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '109943'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (10/14/2010 7:46:38 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRati